This script downloads the synthesis files of third party repositories that you need to define in the program,
and search for a package by the given name.

When you launch the script you will see the follow menu:
------------------	
1 - Search package
2 - Add media
3 - List media
4 - Delete media
------------------

Also, you can launch the script with an argument (the name that you want to search), and you will not
see the above menu but only the search results.


Requirements
-------------

- Python 3
- wget
- gzip
- xz


